00:47:47.250 --> 00:47:52.549
When you look at--when people
look at stock prices they get

00:47:52.549 --> 00:47:55.514
a--it's an illusion.
This is a psychological

00:47:55.514 --> 00:47:57.670
illusion.
They get the sense that there

00:47:57.670 --> 00:48:01.389
are bull markets when the market
