00:48:13.021 --> 00:48:16.349
a famous bull market,
the Roaring 20s.

00:48:16.349 --> 00:48:19.715
You would say,
that just can't be a random

00:48:19.715 --> 00:48:21.582
walk;
it was just going up all the

00:48:21.582 --> 00:48:24.636
time.
Then, this is the 1929 peak and

00:48:24.636 --> 00:48:27.950
