00:49:05.389 --> 00:49:09.748
The random walk theory says
that people are operating under

00:49:09.748 --> 00:49:12.578
illusions;
that there really are no trends

00:49:12.578 --> 00:49:15.130
or there's no way to predict the
market.

00:49:15.130 --> 00:49:17.389
It is just completely
unforecastable.

